    <detaileddescription>
<para>This is a helper base class for writing <computeroutput><ref refid="structMR_1_1BasicUiRenderTask" kindref="compound">BasicUiRenderTask</ref></computeroutput>s that let you click a rectangle in the scene. Note, this task relies on preserving state between the frames. </para>
